{"tid":1174512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最新圓明園銅首驚世曝光","createTime":"2019-05-28T01:50:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T06:45:51.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d1735a2c5abd3f9bdbd18bc8dd6e647b57d3738c","tid":1174512,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T01:50:56.000Z","msg":"著名愛國人士曾憲梓先生雕像揭幕儀式在圓明園三園交界隆重舉行。85歲高齡的曾憲梓先生、中國首飛航天員楊利偉等嘉賓出席了活動。圓明園此舉是為感謝曾憲梓先生對圓明園遺址保護做出的貢獻，傳遞他崇高的愛國主義精神，同時也為了呼籲越來越多的公眾關注圓明園、為圓明園遺址保護添磚加瓦。<br />\n<br />\n  圓明園佔地350公頃，歷史上內外圍牆總長度約為17000延長米，牆高約2.8米。1993年3月，曾憲梓先生看到圓明園圍牆盡毀、遺址滄桑，當即表示捐資800萬元人民幣用於修復圓明園圍牆，搶救、保護圓明園遺址。這筆捐款對圓明園遺址保護起到決定性作用，改變了圓明園當時界限不清的現狀，實現了圓明園「圈起來、清出去、管起來」口號的第一步。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20190524/31408702.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.com.tw%2Farticle%2F20190524%2F31408702.html&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQcFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=a00e7d46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20190524/31408702.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTw0gHvtvsRKeYYdNbaHfDU5mVAPbpsKgAOeSSdlcNsX7yKueQm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcTw0gHvtvsRKeYYdNbaHfDU5mVAPbpsKgAOeSSdlcNsX7yKueQm&h=ba7ecfed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://0.share.photo.xuite.net/bigsilver168/104db0a/11617363/546709687_m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F0.share.photo.xuite.net%2Fbigsilver168%2F104db0a%2F11617363%2F546709687_m.jpg&h=137a5f26&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d1dc903b45f09beb186e17c39fc956a4be1abc7","tid":1174512,"uid":109701,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T01:53:35.000Z","msg":"好快嚟多次八國聯軍 收返埋算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />